Package: rockyIntertidal
Title: Package for importing, joining, and querying NETN rocky intertidal data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Miller", "Kate", , "kathryn_miller@nps.gov", role = c("aut")),
    person("Kozlowski", "Adam", , "adam_kozlowski@nps.gov", role = "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions that import database views from the NETN rocky intertidal backend or exported CSVs from the backend and provides functions to query and summarize NETN rocky intertidal data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/KateMMiller/rockyIntertidal
BugReports: https://github.com/KateMMiller/rockyIntertidal/issues
